{"tid":129734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"師奶偷旺角大家樂膠刀膠叉被捕","createTime":"2017-02-21T22:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T05:46:48.000Z","uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e826a884809ac53964f052813ea58de744a0f4e9","tid":129734,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:21:21.000Z","msg":"女賊旺角偷餐具失手被擒。現場豉油街50號富達大廈，一樓是大家樂快餐店。凌晨3時許，姓李（57歲）保安透過閉路電視目睹1名女子鬼鬼祟祟從後巷潛入，懷疑她有不軌企圖，於是報案。警員到場搜索，於後樓梯截獲一名姓林（44歲）女子，在其攜帶的購物袋搜出一批即棄餐具，包括膠刀及膠叉等。有人辯稱從快餐店擺放後門雜物堆中拿走，警方調查後，以涉嫌企圖盜竊將林拘捕，再帶署扣查。<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170221/bkn-20170221050632793-0221_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170221%2Fbkn-20170221050632793-0221_00822_001.html&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=772d8d98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170221/bkn-20170221050632793-0221_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4b77778e01fe900166c5f760830d83141b44453f","tid":129734,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:26:14.000Z","msg":"入去攞都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5530159412e4f34ac5b87e079480db38a182e73","tid":129734,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入去攞都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一批喎，點入去攞啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6120bf42b82586490dee87d1fb7c842dd7e0d89d","tid":129734,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:47:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49de2399aa19eecad0